<h2>Philosophy</h2>
<p>
   KCPR, Cal Poly's non-profit volunteer-run radio station, 
   provides its listeners with alternative programming which entertains and informs. 
   Programs on KCPR attempt to open local minds to 
   alternative points of view and provide diversity on the airwaves. 
</p>

